span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">SK Penyelenggara Ibadah Haji\r\nKhusus&nbsp; No. D/778/Tahun 2011<o:p></o:p></span></li><li><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">SK Penyelenggara Ibadah\r\nUmroh&nbsp; No. D/169/Tahun 2012<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Annisa Travel juga memiliki\r\nlegalitas resmi Event Organizer dan MICe di bawah anak&nbsp; perusahaan bernama PT. Sigma Mitra Convex.<o:p></o:p></span></p><ul><li><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Surat Izin Usaha Perdagangan\r\n(SIUP) 0512/PM/VI/BPMPTSP/2016<o:p></o:p></span></li><li><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Tanda Daftar Perusahaan\r\n(TDP) 30.06.1.82.12383<o:p></o:p></span></li><li><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-ser